## Attribution

This project is built to complement the "Introduction to Machine Learning Systems" 
textbook by Prof. Vijay Janapa Reddi (Harvard University).

Original Repository: https://github.com/harvard-edge/cs249r_book
Forked Repository: https://github.com/yksanjo/cs249r_book
Textbook Website: https://mlsysbook.ai/

The visualizations are inspired by and designed to support the educational content
in the Machine Learning Systems textbook, originally developed as Harvard University's
CS249r course.

